Change Log
==========



Version 0.2.3: 2024-03-10
-------------------------

Improvements in the table-of-contents creation function:
- Doesn't need a trailing # at the end of the headings any more
- Filters empty links (<a ...></a>) from the heading text (these links can be used as local anchors in the html document)

Bug fixes:
- Trailing // removed from the main navigation links



Version 0.2.2: 2020-05-01
-------------------------

- Fixed: InvalidFullIdentifierError (nanoc version 4.12)
- New rake task remote_test



Version 0.2.1: 2016-10-06
-------------------------

- Changes in article processing:
    - Added author field (if empty, use site author)
    - Tag list not longer mandatory
- Added author and date in the article's HTML header
- Updated new_article rake task



Version 0.2.0: 2016-07-25
-------------------------

- Converted template to nanoc4
- new rake tasks local and remote



Version 0.1.0: 2015-05-10
-------------------------

layouts/redirect.php:
    - Support for encrypted URL's in language redirect script
nanoc.yaml.example:
    - renamed variable "site_title" to "blog_title"

